<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"><head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Kalaallit Nunaat Simulator</title>
  <style>
:root {
  --bg: #efe7da;
  --bg-strong: #e0d5c3;
  --panel: rgba(255, 251, 245, 0.9);
  --panel-strong: rgba(255, 253, 249, 0.97);
  --ink: #342419;
  --muted: #75604d;
  --line: rgba(104, 77, 49, 0.14);
  --shadow: 0 24px 50px rgba(94, 66, 38, 0.13);
  --dem-1: #99b2ff;
  --dem-2: #6990ff;
  --dem-3: #4270f8;
  --dem-4: #1f52ea;
  --rep-1: #ff99a4;
  --rep-2: #ff667c;
  --rep-3: #f73357;
  --rep-4: #e70835;
  --tossup: #e2d7c7;
  --accent: #b06c3a;
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; }
html, body { margin: 0; min-height: 100%; }

body {
  color: var(--ink);
  font-family: "Bahnschrift", "Trebuchet MS", sans-serif;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(176,108,58,0.14), transparent 38%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 85% 90%, rgba(129,100,68,0.10), transparent 34%),
    repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(104,77,49,0.03) 0, rgba(104,77,49,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 96px),
    linear-gradient(180deg, #faf4ec 0%, var(--bg) 42%, var(--bg-strong) 100%);
}

button, input, select { font: inherit; }

.shell {
  width: min(1440px, calc(100% - 2rem));
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 1.25rem 0 2rem;
}

.panel {
  background: var(--panel);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 26px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  min-width: 0;
}

/* ── hero ── */
.hero {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  padding: 1.75rem;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: auto -10% -55% auto;
  width: 340px; height: 340px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(176,108,58,0.18), rgba(176,108,58,0) 72%);
}
.hero::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: -20% auto auto -5%;
  width: 260px; height: 260px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(129,100,68,0.14), rgba(129,100,68,0) 70%);
}

.eyebrow, .panel__eyebrow {
  margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--muted);
}
.hero h1, .panel h2, .score-card__value {
  font-family: "Rockwell", "Cambria", serif;
}
.hero h1 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 4vw, 4rem);
  line-height: 0.95;
  max-width: 12ch;
}
.hero__lede {
  max-width: 62ch;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 1.02rem;
  line-height: 1.55;
}

.hero__copy, .hero__actions { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.hero__actions {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.field { display: grid; gap: 0.45rem; }
.field span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.92rem; }

select, .button {
  border-radius: 16px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(45,30,14,0.16);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  color: var(--ink);
  padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
  transition: transform 160ms ease, border-color 160ms ease, background 160ms ease;
}
select:focus, input[type="range"]:focus, .button:focus {
  outline: 2px solid rgba(31,82,234,0.28);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}
.button {
  cursor: pointer;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.button:hover:not(:disabled) {
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  border-color: rgba(45,30,14,0.28);
}
.button:disabled { cursor: not-allowed; opacity: 0.5; }
.button--accent { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(31,82,234,0.14), rgba(247,51,87,0.18)); }
.button--ghost { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.42); }
.button--blue { background: rgba(66,112,248,0.16); border-color: rgba(66,112,248,0.28); }
.button--red { background: rgba(247,51,87,0.16); border-color: rgba(247,51,87,0.28); }

.hero__buttons {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
  gap: 0.75rem;
}

/* ── layout ── */
.layout {
  margin-top: 1.2rem;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.28fr) minmax(320px, 420px);
  gap: 1rem;
  align-items: start;
}
.map-panel, .sidebar { min-width: 0; }
.map-panel { padding: 1.25rem; position: sticky; top: 1rem; }

#map-status {
  max-width: 42ch;
  min-height: 3.6rem;
}
.map-status__headline, .map-status__line { display: block; }
.map-status__headline { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 700; }
.map-status__line { font-size: 0.82rem; }
.map-status__breakdown {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 0.28rem 0.55rem;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  margin-top: 0.28rem;
}
.map-status__chip {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.34rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.77rem;
  line-height: 1.3;
}
.map-status__dot {
  width: 0.52rem; height: 0.52rem;
  border-radius: 50%;
  flex: 0 0 auto;
}

/* ── map tooltip ── */
.map-tooltip {
  position: absolute;
  z-index: 40;
  min-width: 200px;
  max-width: 270px;
  padding: 0.75rem 0.85rem;
  border-radius: 14px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(45,30,14,0.14);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.97);
  box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(44,27,12,0.16);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.map-tooltip[hidden] { display: none; }
.map-tooltip__title { margin: 0; color: var(--ink); font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 800; }
.map-tooltip__meta { margin: 0.16rem 0 0.55rem; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.78rem; }
.candidate-line {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  padding: 0.22rem 0;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}
.candidate-line__swatch {
  width: 0.7rem; height: 0.7rem;
  border-radius: 50%;
  flex: 0 0 auto;
}
.candidate-line__pct { margin-left: auto; font-weight: 700; }

/* ── sidebar ── */
.sidebar { display: grid; gap: 1rem; }

.panel__header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: start;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.panel__header h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.35rem; }
.panel__note { margin: 0; max-width: 28ch; text-align: right; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.4; }

/* ── map stage ── */
.map-stage {
  position: relative;
  height: clamp(460px, calc(100vh - 135px), 640px);
  border-radius: 26px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid rgba(104,77,49,0.12);
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(249,240,229,0.94), rgba(237,226,211,0.94));
}
.map-shell {
  height: 100%;
  min-height: 0;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 0.4rem 0;
}
.map-shell svg {
  width: auto;
  max-width: 100%;
  max-height: calc(100% - 0.8rem);
  height: auto;
  display: block;
  shape-rendering: geometricPrecision;
}
.map-shell path {
  transition: fill 220ms ease;
  cursor: pointer;
  stroke: #111;
  stroke-width: 0.9px;
  vector-effect: non-scaling-stroke;
}
.map-shell path:hover { opacity: 0.82; }
.map-shell path.selected { stroke: var(--ink); stroke-width: 1.5px; }

.map-toolbar {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
}
.map-footer {
  margin-top: 0.55rem;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}
.map-footnote { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.78rem; max-width: 50ch; line-height: 1.4; }

/* ── vote strip ── */
.vote-strip-wrap { margin-top: 1rem; }
.vote-strip-label {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
}
.vote-strip {
  height: 1.4rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  overflow: hidden;
  display: flex;
  border: 1px solid rgba(45,30,14,0.1);
}
.vote-strip__seg {
  height: 100%;
  transition: width 400ms cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
  position: relative;
}

/* ── score panel ── */
.score-panel { padding: 1.25rem; }
.score-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
}
.score-card {
  padding: 0.75rem 0.9rem;
  border-radius: 16px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(45,30,14,0.08);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.48);
}
/* party colors */
:root {
  --ppd: #d92a2a; --ppd-bg: rgba(217,42,42,0.09); --ppd-border: rgba(217,42,42,0.2);
  --pnp: #1a52c7; --pnp-bg: rgba(26,82,199,0.09); --pnp-border: rgba(26,82,199,0.2);
  --mvc: #7c3aed; --mvc-bg: rgba(124,58,237,0.09); --mvc-border: rgba(124,58,237,0.2);
  --pip: #15803d; --pip-bg: rgba(21,128,61,0.09);  --pip-border: rgba(21,128,61,0.2);
  --pd:  #c2692a; --pd-bg:  rgba(194,105,42,0.09); --pd-border:  rgba(194,105,42,0.2);
}
.score-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }
.score-card--ppd { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ppd-bg), rgba(255,255,255,0.7)); border-color: var(--ppd-border); }
.score-card--pnp { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pnp-bg), rgba(255,255,255,0.7)); border-color: var(--pnp-border); }
.score-card--mvc { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--mvc-bg), rgba(255,255,255,0.7)); border-color: var(--mvc-border); }
.score-card--pip { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pip-bg), rgba(255,255,255,0.7)); border-color: var(--pip-border); }
.score-card--pd  { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pd-bg),  rgba(255,255,255,0.7)); border-color: var(--pd-border);  }
.score-card__label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin: 0 0 0.1rem; }
.score-card__value { font-size: 1.7rem; line-height: 1; margin: 0; }
.score-card--ppd .score-card__value { color: var(--ppd); }
.score-card--pnp .score-card__value { color: var(--pnp); }
.score-card--mvc .score-card__value { color: var(--mvc); }
.score-card--pip .score-card__value { color: var(--pip); }
.score-card--pd  .score-card__value { color: var(--pd);  }
.score-card__sub { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.15rem; }

.winner-banner {
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
  padding: 0.65rem 1rem;
  border-radius: 14px;
  text-align: center;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1rem;
  transition: background 300ms ease;
}
.winner-banner--ppd { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ppd-bg), rgba(255,200,200,0.2)); color: #6b0f0f; }
.winner-banner--pnp { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pnp-bg), rgba(180,210,255,0.2)); color: #0c2360; }
.winner-banner--mvc { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--mvc-bg), rgba(220,200,255,0.2)); color: #3b1578; }
.winner-banner--pip { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pip-bg), rgba(180,240,200,0.2)); color: #0a3d1f; }
.winner-banner--pd  { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pd-bg),  rgba(255,220,180,0.2)); color: #5c2d0a; }
.winner-banner--tie { background: rgba(200,139,45,0.15); color: #5a3c10; }
.winner-sub { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.2rem; }

/* region boost grid: 3 cols × 2 rows */
.region-actions { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr !important; }

/* ── controls panel ── */
.controls-panel { padding: 1.25rem; }
.slider-group { display: grid; gap: 0.75rem; margin-top: 0.75rem; }
.slider-row { display: grid; gap: 0.25rem; }
.slider-row__top {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: baseline;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
}
.slider-row__label { font-weight: 600; }
.slider-row__val { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.82rem; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; min-width: 3.5ch; text-align: right; }
input[type="range"] {
  width: 100%;
  accent-color: var(--dem-4);
  cursor: pointer;
}

/* ── region panel ── */
.region-panel { padding: 1.25rem; }
.region-panel.is-hidden { display: none; }
.region-actions { display: grid; gap: 0.5rem; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }

/* ── close races ── */
.close-races-panel { padding: 1.25rem; }
.races-list { display: grid; gap: 0.45rem; margin-top: 0.6rem; }
.race-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem;
  border-radius: 10px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  border: 1px solid rgba(45,30,14,0.07);
}
.race-item__name { flex: 1; font-weight: 600; }
.race-item__margin { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); }
.race-item__swatch { width: 0.55rem; height: 0.55rem; border-radius: 50%; flex: 0 0 auto; }

/* ── vote pie ── */
.vote-pie-wrap {
  width: 100%;
  display: grid;
  justify-items: center;
  gap: 0.55rem;
  margin: 0.75rem 0 0.25rem;
}
.vote-pie {
  position: relative;
  width: min(100%, 214px);
  aspect-ratio: 1;
}
.vote-pie__svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; display: block; overflow: visible; }
.vote-pie__slice {
  stroke: rgba(255,251,244,0.88);
  stroke-width: 2.5;
  transition: transform 120ms ease, filter 120ms ease;
  transform-origin: center;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.vote-pie__slice:hover, .vote-pie__slice:focus { transform: scale(1.05); filter: saturate(1.1) brightness(1.03); }
.vote-pie__readout { width: min(100%, 214px); display: grid; gap: 0.16rem; text-align: center; padding: 0.1rem 0 0; }
.vote-pie__eyebrow { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.7rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin: 0; }
.vote-pie__label { font-family: "Rockwell","Cambria",serif; font-size: 1.05rem; margin: 0; line-height: 1.2; }
.vote-pie__share { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 0; }

/* ── party panel ── */
.party-panel { padding: 1.25rem; }
.party-list { display: grid; gap: 0.75rem; margin-top: 0.75rem; }
.party-card {
  padding: 0.75rem 0.9rem;
  border-radius: 14px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(104,77,49,0.12);
  background: rgba(255,253,249,0.72);
}
.party-card__top {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
}
.party-palette-preview { display: flex; gap: 0.3rem; }
.party-palette-preview span {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 1.1rem; height: 1.1rem;
  border-radius: 4px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}
.party-remove {
  background: none;
  border: 1px solid rgba(45,30,14,0.15);
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1;
  padding: 0.15rem 0.45rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  transition: background 120ms, color 120ms;
}
.party-remove:hover { background: rgba(220,60,60,0.1); color: #c00; border-color: rgba(200,50,50,0.3); }
.party-fields { display: grid; gap: 0.45rem; }
.party-field { display: grid; gap: 0.2rem; font-size: 0.82rem; }
.party-field span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.78rem; }
.party-field input[type="range"] { width: 100%; accent-color: var(--accent); }
.party-field input[type="text"] {
  padding: 0.3rem 0.5rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(45,30,14,0.15);
  border-radius: 8px;
  background: rgba(255,253,249,0.9);
  font: inherit;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
}
.party-field--color { flex-direction: row; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; display: flex; }
.party-field--color span { flex: 1; }
.party-field--color input[type="color"] { width: 2.5rem; height: 1.8rem; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid rgba(45,30,14,0.15); cursor: pointer; padding: 1px; }
.party-field__row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
.party-section {
  border: 1px solid rgba(104,77,49,0.12);
  border-radius: 10px;
  margin-top: 0.35rem;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.party-section__head {
  padding: 0.38rem 0.6rem;
  font-size: 0.76rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--muted);
  cursor: pointer;
  user-select: none;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.35rem;
  background: rgba(104,77,49,0.05);
}
.party-section__head::before { content: "▶"; font-size: 0.6rem; transition: transform 140ms; }
details[open] > .party-section__head::before { transform: rotate(90deg); }
.party-section__body { padding: 0.45rem 0.55rem; display: grid; gap: 0.35rem; }
.party-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 0.75rem; }
.party-actions .button { flex: 1; font-size: 0.82rem; }
.region-actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
.region-actions .button { flex: 1; min-width: 3.5rem; }

/* ── back link ── */
.back-link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.4rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  padding: 0.35rem 0.6rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
  transition: color 140ms ease, background 140ms ease;
}
.back-link:hover { color: var(--ink); background: rgba(0,0,0,0.04); }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .hero__actions { flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .hero__buttons { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="shell">
  <a href="index.html" class="back-link">← All States</a>

  <!-- hero -->
  <div class="hero panel">
    <div class="hero__copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Greenland · Municipal Party Map</p>
      <h1>Kalaallit Nunaat Simulator</h1>
      <p class="hero__lede">
        Build alternate coalition maps across Greenland's five municipalities.
        Tune real-world party ideology, funding, turnout pull, buzz, party strength, age coalitions,
        and regional strength, then test how the islandwide popular vote shifts municipality by municipality.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__actions">
      <div class="field">
        <span>Scenario Preset</span>
        <select id="preset-select">
          <option value="">-- choose preset --</option>
          <option value="baseline">2025 Local Baseline</option>
          <option value="demokraatit-surge">Demokraatit Surge</option>
          <option value="ia-comeback">IA Comeback</option>
          <option value="siumut-machine">Siumut Machine</option>
          <option value="naleraq-breakthrough">Naleraq Breakthrough</option>
          <option value="quiet-cycle">Quiet Cycle</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="hero__buttons">
        <button id="apply-preset" class="button button--accent">Apply</button>
        <button id="reroll-button" class="button button--ghost">Reroll</button>
        <button id="reset-button" class="button button--ghost">Reset</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="layout">
    <!-- left: map -->
    <div class="map-panel panel">
      <div class="panel__header">
        <div>
          <p class="panel__eyebrow">Municipality Map</p>
          <h2>Greenland</h2>
        </div>
        <p id="map-status" class="panel__note"><span class="map-status__headline">5 municipalities loaded</span><span class="map-status__line">Projected turnout: 21,450 valid votes islandwide.</span><span class="map-status__breakdown"><span class="map-status__chip"><span class="map-status__dot" style="background:#d2353f;"></span>SIU 39.0%</span><span class="map-status__chip"><span class="map-status__dot" style="background:#2365d1;"></span>DEM 30.8%</span><span class="map-status__chip"><span class="map-status__dot" style="background:#2b8a57;"></span>IA 19.1%</span></span></p>
      </div>

